Package: lacunaRity
Type: Package
Title: Fast 3D Lacunarity for LiDAR Voxel Data
Version: 0.0.01
Date: 2023-09-25
Authors@R: person("Elliott", "Smeds",
  email = "elliott.alfred93@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1054-7491"))
URL: https://github.com/ElliottSmeds/lacunaRity
BugReports: https://github.com/ElliottSmeds/lacunaRity/issues
Description: Calculates lacunarity curves for 3D voxel data using a fast version 
    of the gliding-box algorithm implemented in C++. Gliding-box lacunarity can 
    be calculated using the traditional fixed-boundary algorithm or the 
    periodic-boundary algorithm introduced by Feagin et al 2006.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
